review_text: 24 hours Parking: wide

Restoran KFC Kisamaun Daan Mogot Tangerang memiliki suasana yang bersih dan nyaman. Tempatnya cukup luas dan terdapat beberapa meja dan kursi untuk dine-in. Tersedia juga area outdoor yang cocok untuk bersantai sambil menikmati ayam goreng KFC. Menu: KFC Kisamaun Daan Mogot Tangerang menawarkan berbagai macam menu ayam goreng khas KFC, seperti KFC Bucket, Colonel Burger, dan Twister. Selain itu, terdapat juga menu lain seperti nasi, kentang goreng, dan dessert. Harga: Harga makanan di KFC Kisamaun Daan Mogot Tangerang cukup terjangkau dan sesuai dengan kualitasnya. Anda bisa menikmati ayam goreng KFC dengan harga mulai dari Rp20.000 - Rp50.000. Rasa: Rasa ayam goreng KFC Kisamaun Daan Mogot Tangerang tidak perlu diragukan lagi. Ayamnya selalu renyah dan bumbunya meresap dengan baik. Kentang gorengnya juga gurih dan renyah. Pelayanan: Pelayanan di KFC Kisamaun Daan Mogot Tangerang cukup ramah dan cepat. Para pelayannya sigap dan membantu dalam memilih menu. Kelebihan: - Ayam goreng renyah dan lezat - Pelayanan ramah dan cepat - Harga terjangkau - Tempat bersih dan nyaman - Lokasi strategis Kekurangan: - Terkadang bisa ramai, terutama pada jam makan siang - Menu yang monoton Kesimpulan: KFC Kisamaun Daan Mogot Tangerang adalah tempat yang tepat untuk menikmati ayam goreng KFC yang renyah dan lezat dengan pelayanan yang ramah. Cocok untuk makan bersama keluarga, teman, atau pasangan.
review_translated_text: The KFC Kisamaun Daan Mogot Tangerang restaurant has a clean and comfortable atmosphere. The place is quite spacious and there are several tables and chairs for dine-in. There is also an outdoor area which is suitable for relaxing while enjoying KFC fried chicken. Menu: KFC Kisamaun Daan Mogot Tangerang offers a variety of typical KFC fried chicken menus, such as KFC Bucket, Colonel Burger, and Twister. Apart from that, there are also other menus such as rice, fried potatoes and dessert. Price: Food prices at KFC Kisamaun Daan Mogot Tangerang are quite affordable and commensurate with the quality. You can enjoy KFC fried chicken with prices starting from IDR 20,000 - IDR 50,000. Taste: The taste of KFC Kisamaun Daan Mogot Tangerang fried chicken cannot be doubted. The chicken is always crispy and the spices blend well. The fried potatoes are also tasty and crunchy. Service: The service at KFC Kisamaun Daan Mogot Tangerang is quite friendly and fast. The waiters were alert and helpful in choosing the menu. Excess: - Crispy and delicious fried chicken - Friendly and fast service - Affordable prices - Clean and comfortable place - Strategic location Lack: - Can be busy sometimes, especially at lunch time - Monotonous menu Conclusion: KFC Kisamaun Daan Mogot Tangerang is the right place to enjoy crispy and delicious KFC fried chicken with friendly service. Suitable for eating with family, friends or couples.

review_translated_text: First time to this branch. Since the ground floor was full, we were directed upstairs. The table is a bit dirty. Only 1 plug. In the bathroom there are chicken bones. There is no hand wash, there is only Giv bar soap above the toilet seat where people seem reluctant to use bar soap. There is a prayer place in front of the toilet. Super busy atmosphere. But the service is total. I order : 1. Rice with crushed chicken with chili sauce 2. Indomie corned beef 3. Tomato juice 4. Iced cappuccino All total 85,000

review_translated_text: Super long service, especially when ordering Indomie. Its taking so long to complain and Im already lazy... Ordered corned egg indomie, Ive been waiting for a long time but the corned beef is out of stock, and without any information up front, I just made egg noodles without corned beef, Im a bit disappointed... And the texture of the noodles feels soft and overdone, and the soup is no longer hot... For toast, its okay, there are lots of variants. Please improve the service and food quality... Its a shame that this cafe has been around for so long... back in the day it wasnt this bad.

Meskipun porsinya terlihat sedikit lebih kecil dari yang disajikan di piring, rasanya tetap menggugah selera. Pertama-tama, mari bahas tentang kentang goreng + sosis. Sosisnya memiliki cita rasa yang khas dan kenyal, sementara kentang gorengnya renyah di luar dan lembut di dalam. Kombinasi ini memberikan sentuhan yang berbeda dan menyenangkan bagi lidah. Yang menarik adalah porsi esnya yang cukup besar, membuatnya menjadi pilihan yang tepat jika ingin menikmati minuman sejuk untuk waktu yang lama. Pilihan ini sangat cocok untuk menemani nongkrong bersama sahabat atau kerabat, terutama jika Anda berencana untuk menghabiskan waktu lebih lama di tempat ini. Ruangan ber-AC memberikan kenyamanan untuk menikmati hidangan di dalam ruangan yang sejuk, sementara area outdoor cocok bagi mereka yang ingin menikmati udara segar sambil menikmati makanan. Secara keseluruhan, Roti Bakar 88 di Pasar Lama menawarkan pengalaman kuliner yang menyenangkan. Meskipun porsi kentang goreng + sosis terlihat lebih kecil, rasanya yang unik membuatnya layak dicoba. Thai Tea yang lezat dengan es yang cukup banyak menjadi pelengkap yang sempurna. review_translated_text: Roti Bakar 88 at Pasar Lama, Jl Kisamaun No. 118, offers a unique culinary experience with an interesting menu variety. I just visited this place and ordered fries + sausage, an interesting combination with a different look from other 88 toasties. Even though the portion looks a little smaller than what is served on the plate, the taste is still appetizing. First, lets talk about fries + sausage. Even though the portion looks smaller than what is served on the plate, the taste is truly unique. The sausage has a distinctive and chewy taste, while the fries are crispy on the outside and soft on the inside. This combination provides a different and pleasant touch to the tongue. Even though the portion may look smaller, the taste makes me want to come back to try other menu items. I also tried Thai Tea there, and the taste was really satisfying. This drink has a rich tea flavor with just the right touch of sweetness. Whats interesting is that the portion of ice is quite large, making it the right choice if you want to enjoy a cool drink for a long time. This choice is very suitable to accompany hanging out with friends or relatives, especially if you plan to spend more time at this place. This place offers a comfortable atmosphere with seating options both inside the air-conditioned room and in the outdoor area for smokers. I found the seating placement to be quite good, giving diners flexibility according to their individual preferences. The air-conditioned room provides the comfort of enjoying a meal in a cool room, while the outdoor area is suitable for those who want to enjoy fresh air while enjoying their meal. Overall, Roti Bakar 88 at Pasar Lama offers a pleasant culinary experience. Even though the portion of fries + sausage looks smaller, the unique taste makes it worth trying. Delicious Thai Tea with plenty of ice is the perfect complement. With comfortable seating options and a friendly atmosphere, this place is a good choice for hanging out with friends or family. I highly recommend this place to those looking for a unique menu variety and want to enjoy a fun atmosphere.

Menjelang malam tahun baru, Serba Food pasang LIVE MUSIC di bagian outdoor. Suasananya masi sama, tetep comfy buat nongki bareng keluarga dan temen-temen. Pelayanannya oke dan ramah. . Ai pesen: Sapi Hotplate Mongolia Satu kata: ENAAAAK! Dagingnya juicy, teksturnya lembut banget dan ga nge-lawan pas dikunyah. Warbiasah! Bumbu lada hitam berasa banget, nge-blend dengan sempurna dengan potongan bawang bombaynya. Porsiannya lumayan banyak. . Pakcoy 2 Rasa Ini ga kalah makyusnya, selalu REPEAT ORDER! Daun Pakcoynya bisa se-renyah itu dan rasanya gurih. Batang Pakcoynya pun manis dan lembut. Wajib pesen kalau makan disini . Gurame Telor Asin Pilihnya bagian tengah ke ekor. Gorengnya bagus, ga oily. Bagian luarnya renyah dan daging guramenya lembut, ga amis, serta wangi daun jeruknya. Saus telor asinnya juga enak, rasa asinnya PAS. Dalam satu pax, dapet nasi, salad, potongan gurame telor asin dan kuah telor. Kuah telornya lumayan tasty. . Ayam Lady Boy Katanya ayamnya digoreng dulu baru dipanggang. Kulitnya renyah dan daging ayamnya empuk. Bisa pilih bagian dada atau paha. Satu porsi, dapet nasi, sambel, telor dadar, ayam dan kuah bening. Lumayan lah ga seret jadinya hehehe. . Lemongrass Ice Tea Teh serehnya enak, wangi serehnya kerasa banget. Nikmat. . Tahu Enoki (Rp 40K) Tahunya dicampur dengan jamur enoki lembut dan kuah coklatnya enak. Suka banget! Satu porsi isi 4 potong tahu lumutnya dan ada potongan pakcoy. . Ayam Ibu Tiri (Rp 60K) Seperti ayam cabe lada garam. Ayam fillet dipotong memanjang dan digoreng tepung. Ada campuran kacang, potongan cabe dan daun bawang. Rasanya gurih dan teksturnya empuk. Cuman kurang nampol aja bumbunya dan kurang tercampur dengan baik lada garamnya. Didominasi dengan rasa pedas lada. . Tahu Telor Asin (Rp 45K) Kesan pertama enak dan gurih tapi kalau kebanyakan agak mabok dan eneg juga. Renyah dan saus telor asinnya berasa banget. Ada potongan cabe merahnya dan agak pedas. . Onde Naiwong Pandan (Rp 28K) My favorite! Satu porsi isi 3 bulatan dan disajikan masih panas. Bentuknya lumayan besar dengan isian kacang ijo yang sudah dilembutkan. Renyah di luar dan enak pas digigit! . Es Teh Tawar (Rp 10K) : ga bisa REFILL gaes!
review_translated_text: Towards New Years Eve, Serba Food put on LIVE MUSIC in the outdoor section. The atmosphere is still the same, its still comfortable for hanging out with family and friends. The service is okay and friendly. . Ai messaged: Mongolian Hotplate Beef One word: ENAAAAK! The meat is juicy, the texture is very soft and doesnt resist when chewed. Be wary! The black pepper seasoning is really delicious, it blends perfectly with the chopped onions. The portion is quite large. . Pakchoy 2 Flavors This is no less important, always REPEAT ORDER! Pakcoy leaves can be that crunchy and taste delicious. The Pakchoy stems are also sweet and soft. You must order if you eat here . Salted Egg Gurami Select the middle part to the tail. The frying is good, not oily. The outside is crispy and the gourami meat is soft, not fishy, and smells good of lime leaves. The salted egg sauce is also delicious, the salty taste is PERFECT. In one pax, you get rice, salad, pieces of salted egg gourami and egg sauce. The egg soup is quite tasty. . Lady Boy Chicken They say the chicken is fried first and then grilled. The skin is crispy and the chicken meat is tender. You can choose the chest or thighs. One portion, get rice, chili sauce, omelette, chicken and clear sauce. Its not bad that it doesnt drag, hehehe. . Lemongrass Ice Tea The lemongrass tea is delicious, the lemongrass smells really good. Enjoyment. . Enoki Tofu (Rp. 40K) The tofu is mixed with soft enoki mushrooms and the chocolate sauce is delicious. Really like! One portion contains 4 pieces of moss tofu and pieces of pak choy. . Stepmothers Chicken (Rp. 60K) Like salt pepper chili chicken. Chicken fillet is cut lengthwise and fried in flour. There is a mixture of nuts, chopped chilies and spring onions. The taste is delicious and the texture is soft. Its just that the seasoning isnt enough and the salt and pepper arent mixed well. Dominated by the spicy taste of pepper. . Salted Egg Tofu (Rp. 45K) The first impression is that it is delicious and tasty, but if you eat too much, its a bit drunk and uncomfortable too. Its crunchy and the salted egg sauce really tastes good. There are pieces of red chili and its a bit spicy. . Onde Naiwong Pandan (Rp. 28K) My favourite! One portion contains 3 circles and is served still hot. The shape is quite large and filled with softened green beans. Crispy on the outside and delicious when you bite into it! . Fresh Iced Tea (Rp. 10K): cant REFILL, guys!

review_text: Review berdasarkan kunjungan kami di tanggal 9 September  2023. Kami memesan mix pork rice Dan fish n chips. Mix pork rice nya cukup enak, nasi nya hambar, tertolong kalau dituang kecap pelengkap nya, sajian topping daging pork nya cukup mengenyangkan. Kuah kaldu yang diberikan kurang berguna, hanya seperti air diberi lada. Fish n chips nya kurang memuaskan. Bentuk fish nya gendut-gendut seperti pisang molen, hanya tebal di tepung saja dan hambar. Kentang goreng nya lebih lumayan karena menggunakan merek kentang yang sudah coated, sehingga garing nya pas. Overall untuk harga dan rasa nya, fish n chips nya sangat tidak kami rekomendasikan. Parking: Parkir di area parkir Mall The Breeze Wheelchair accessibility: Ada 2 anak tangga untuk masuk ke Restoran. Kursi roda harus diangkat.
review_translated_text: Review based on our visit on September 9, 2023. We ordered mix pork rice and fish n chips. The mixed pork rice is quite delicious, the rice is bland, it helps if you add the complementary soy sauce, the pork topping is quite filling. The broth that is given is not useful, its just like water with pepper. The fish n chips were not satisfying. The shape of the fish is fat like banana molen, only thick in flour and tasteless. The fries are better because they use a brand of coated potatoes, so they are just right. Overall, for the price and taste, we really dont recommend the fish n chips. Parking: Park in The Breeze Mall parking area Wheelchair accessibility: There are 2 stairs to enter the restaurant. The wheelchair must be lifted.

My wife and I ordered some drinks, I had the kiwi mojito, and she had the litchee tea, which, aside from it being water syrup with cut fruit in it, also lacked taste. Not the worst place weve been to, but also not memorable.

review_text: Lagi main didaerah Cipondoh, Tangerang mampir ke outlet mungil yaitu Campsis yang konon artinya bunga. Tempatnya memang hanya menempati ruko kecil berkonsep lebih ke to go, namun ada sekitar 4 kursi untuk sekedar nunggu pesanan. Aku mencoba menu: 1. Buah Siram Buah yang dipakai yaitu pisang, anggur, strawberry, semangka dan melon. Untuk buahnya fresh manis asam yang enak disiram saus coklat pure yang lumer. 2. Fruit Jelly Ball Jelly berbentuk bulat dengan rasa anggur dan melon didalam jelly nya ada topping buah asli yang teksturnya kenyal dan segar, kuahnya pakai cheese milk yang manisnya pas. 3. Es Kul Kul Buah yang dipakai yaitu strawberry, semangka dan kurma. Bentuknya seperti sate, buahnya fresh dan disiram saus coklat yang rasanya manis dan lumer. 4. Puding Pandan Rasa pudingnya oke terasa sekali pandannya dan manisnya pun pas. 5. Butterscoth Coffee Rasa kopinya light sangat tipis lebih dominan manis, jadi rasanya kurang balance.
review_translated_text: While playing in the Cipondoh area, Tangerang stopped by a small outlet, Campsis, which is said to mean flower. The place only occupies a small shophouse with a more to go concept, but there are around 4 chairs for just waiting for orders. I tried the menu: 1. Flush Fruit The fruits used are bananas, grapes, strawberries, watermelon and melon. The fresh, sweet and sour fruit is delicious, drizzled with melted pure chocolate sauce. 2. Fruit Jelly Balls The jelly is round in shape with the taste of grapes and melon. Inside the jelly there is a real fruit topping which has a chewy and fresh texture, the sauce uses cheese milk which is just the right amount of sweetness. 3. Ice Kul Kul The fruits used are strawberries, watermelon and dates. The shape is like satay, the fruit is fresh and drizzled with chocolate sauce which tastes sweet and melts. 4. Pandan Pudding The taste of the pudding is really good, it really tastes like pandan and the sweetness is just right. 5. Butterscotch Coffee The taste of the coffee is light, very thin and dominantly sweet, so the taste is not balanced.

As for the place itself, its not too big, just right for around 8-10 people and even then its a bit cramped hehe, but the wifi is fast, and the room is air-conditioned, clean, comfortable, quiet. review_text: Assalamu alikum semoga kita dalam Lindungan Allah dan selalu sehat dan bahagia, sholawat serta Salam semoga terlimpah curah kepada Junjungan Nabi Besar kita Muhammad SAW. Rumah Makan Sari Banten yang terletak didaerah Cipare Kota Serang ini cukup bagus bagi rombongan besar yang akan berkunjung disini ada Musollah yang cukup bersih juga Toilet. Tempatnya nampak terlihat sepi bila di lihat dari jalan raya, namun ketika memasuki nya cukup luas tempat parkirnya juga banyak pepohonan cukup besar sehingga bisa untuk menambah suasana teduh. Untuk makanan yang dipesan yaitu nasi timbelnya biasa saja tidak ada kelebihan khusus sama dengan nasi timbel ditempat lainnya. Di iringi musik yang tamu-tamu dipersilahkan bila ingin menyanyi. Rumah Makan Sari Banten ini menyediakan menu makanan ala Sunda. Alumni STM Negeri Serang pada tgl 10 Februari 2024 mengadakan Reuni Kecil dengan yang hadir 30 orang. Semoga Alumni STM Negeri Serang tahun 1995 selalu sehat dan membawa keberkahan, Aamiin
review_translated_text: Assalamualikum, may we be in the protection of Allah and always healthy and happy, prayers and greetings may be abundantly poured out upon our Great Prophet Muhammad SAW. The Sari Banten Restaurant, which is located in the Cipare area of Serang City, is quite good for large groups who will visit here. There is a Musollah which is quite clean as well as the toilets. The place looks quiet when viewed from the main road, but when you enter the parking area is quite spacious and there are lots of large trees so it can add to the shady atmosphere. For the food ordered, the Nasi Timbel is just ordinary, there are no special advantages to the Nasi Timbel in other places. Accompanied by music, guests are welcome if they want to sing. Sari Banten Restaurant provides a Sundanese style food menu. Alumni of STM Negeri Serang on February 10 2024 held a Small Reunion with 30 people attending. Hopefully the Serang State STM Alumni of 1995 will always be healthy and bring blessings, Aamiin

review_text: Assalamu alaikum semoga kita dalam lindungan Allah, selalu sehat dan bahagia, Aamiin. Alumni STM Negeri Serang angkatan 1995 mengadakan pertemuan atau kumpulan pada tgl 10 Februari 2024 di Rumah Makan Sari Banten Cipare Kota Serang. Acaranya dari jam 11.00 sampai dengan selesai, kami memesan makanan dan telah tersedia hidangan nasi timbel, namun sebelum makan kita memesan kopi terlebih dahulu, baru sekitar jam 12.00 kita dipersilahkan makan. Nasi timbelnya ada yang pakai ayam goreng dan ada yang lauknya ikan bandeng alias pecak bandeng dengan sayur asem. Rumah Makan Sari Banten ini menyediakan menu makanan khas Sunda. Ada juga hiburannya dengan organ tunggal sebagai penghantar atau mungkin pemghangat suasana saja. Toilet juga tempat parkir di Rumah Makan Sari Banten ini cukup luas juga terdapat Musollah yang cukup bagus mungkin karena Musollah ini nampaknya belum lama dibangun. Terdapat juga pohon-pohon cukup besar diaekitaran Rumah Makan Sari Banten ini. Semoga Allah selalu memberikan kesehatan serta Rizki yang Barokah dari Allah untuk para Alimni STM Negeri Serang Angkatan 1995, Aamiin
review_translated_text: Assalamualaikum, may we be protected by Allah, always healthy and happy, Aamiin. STM Negeri Serang alumni class of 1995 held a meeting or gathering on February 10 2024 at the Sari Banten Cipare Restaurant, Serang City. The event was from 11.00 until the end, we ordered food and the nasi timbel dish was available, but before eating we ordered coffee first, only around 12.00 we were invited to eat. Some of the Nasi Timbel uses fried chicken and some have milkfish as a side dish, aka pecak milkfish with tamarind vegetables. Sari Banten Restaurant provides a typical Sundanese food menu. There is also entertainment with a single organ as a conductor or perhaps just to warm up the atmosphere. The toilets and parking area at the Sari Banten Restaurant are quite spacious and there is also a Musollah which is quite good, perhaps because the Musollah doesnt look like it was built long ago. There are also quite large trees around the Sari Banten Restaurant. May Allah always give health and blessings from Allah to the Alimni of STM Negeri Serang Class of 1995, Aamiin

review_text: Booking untuk bukber & acara bridal shower,, 1. Booking by whatsapp dri h-2 slwrespon, bahkan di hari H nya admin nya bikin emosii perkara tempat&menu yg super gajelaaaaaaas. 2. Biasanya kalo booking untuk bukber pas kita sampe ga lama lagi menu semua siap, ini pas mau magrib baru minum aja itupun belum ready smua minum nya,  penyajian nya yg super lama sampe beberapa kali nanyaa untuk mastiin kapan ready, makanan ready nya satu persatuuu dlm wktu yg cukup lama,, bahkan sampe jam 9kurang baru bisa di bilang ready semua untuk makanan&dessertnya. Gila sih ampe ga mood semua nyaa, untung nya ke bantuu acara bridal shower  jdi ga bt bt amat ni tmpt.
review_translated_text: Booking for bukber & bridal shower event,, 1. Booked by WhatsApp from day 2, no response, even on the day the admin made us emotional about the place & menu which was super funny. 2. Usually if you order for bukber when we arrive it wont be long before the menu is all ready, this is when its just about sunset, just drink it and even then not all the drinks are ready, the serving takes so long that you ask several times to make sure when its ready, the food is ready one by one. It took quite a long time, even until less than 9 oclock before we could say everyone was ready for the food & dessert. Its crazy that everyones not in the mood, luckily I was there to help with the bridal shower so it wasnt too bad.

review_text: Kenapa saya kasih ratingnya agak kurang bagus? 1. Kami reservasi untuk buka puasa dari jam 2 siang untuk di indoor... Jam 5 sore tbtb di tawarkan outdoor (yang mana kami semua sudah jalan ke lokasi karena mempertimbangkan jarak dan kemacetan) 2. Sampai di lokasi kami melihat meja dengan nama diatasnya (benar itu atas nama yang kami reservasi) ternyata..... Pihak resto mengatakan bahwa meja itu milik orang lain, kami di siapkan lokasi indoor dengan meja panjang yang ditutupi kain hitam. Karena terkesan horror kami memilih di outdoor. 3. Kami pesan makanan pukul 17.30 (waktu tertera pada bill) karena momen ramadhan minuman datang pukul 17.50 (karena kami pesan air mineral kemasan). 4. Kami sholat magrib dan berharap makanan datang setelahnya... Tapi makanan datang pukul 19.00. 5. Pesan thaitea tidak layak konsumsi, bau menyengat seperti obat dan rasa yang asam. Memang di ganti minuman baru, tapi sudah kami konsumsi walupun sedikit dan menyebabkan sakit perut. 6. Rice bowl chicken teriyaki ada semut merah besar seperti semut rangrang (bilang mau diganti, sampai kurang lebih 40 menit tidak juga di ganti) 7. Pesan mie godok 1 jam belum datang, sampai kami ke kasir dan payment baru bilang sedang dibuatkan dan akhirnya take away karena terlalu lama. 8. Pelayanan kurang cepat dan terkesan seperti mengabaikan. Memang diakhir kami diberikan kompensasi berupa diskon. Tapi, hal tersebut tidak membuat kami senang. Kami tetap kecewa diskon yang diberikan tidak setara dengan hal yang kami alami , binatang di makanan (sakit perut, mual dan muntah akibat Thaitea yang sudah tidak layak konsumsi *basi*) Mohon untuk lebih diperhatikan kembali, untuk mengecek kelayakan bahan makanan dan minuman serta mengecek berkala expired date untuk semua bahan masakan. Saya tidak bermaksud untuk menjatuhkan, saya hanya memberikan kritik dan saran untuk pihak resto. Terimakasih
review_translated_text: Why did I give it a slightly less good rating? 1. We made a reservation to break the fast from 2 pm for indoor... At 5 pm tbtb it was offered outdoors (which we all had to walk to the location considering the distance and traffic jams) 2. When we arrived at the location, we saw a table with a name on it (thats true, it was in the name we had reserved). Turns out... The restaurant said that the table belonged to someone else, we were prepared in an indoor location with a long table covered with a black cloth. Because it seemed scary, we chose outdoor. 3. We ordered food at 17.30 (the time stated on the bill) because during Ramadan the drinks came at 17.50 (because we ordered bottled mineral water). 4. We prayed Maghrib and hoped that the food would come after... But the food came at 19.00. 5. The Thaitea message is not suitable for consumption, the smell is strong like medicine and the taste is sour. It was replaced with a new drink, but we consumed even a little and it caused stomach ache. 6. Rice bowl chicken teriyaki had big red ants like weaver ants (said they wanted to replace them, they still didnt change them for about 40 minutes) 7. The order for godok noodles didnt arrive for 1 hour, until we went to the cashier and paid before we said it was being made and finally took it away because it took too long. 8. Service is not fast enough and gives the impression of neglect. Indeed, at the end we were given compensation in the form of a discount. However, this did not make us happy. We are still disappointed that the discount given is not equivalent to what we experienced, animals in food (stomach ache, nausea and vomiting due to Thaitea which is no longer suitable for consumption *stale*) Please pay more attention to check the suitability of food and drink ingredients and periodically check the expiry date for all cooking ingredients. I dont mean to bring down, I just provide criticism and suggestions for the restaurant. Thank You

Saya kesini tanggal 27 April 2024 sekitar jam 10 pagi karna kebetulan lagi berlibur di Serang plus cafe ini yang paling dekat dari hotel. Tempatnya cozy, banyak spot instagramable, dan luaass banget. Menunya cukup variatif dan harganya juga affordable. Saya order quesadilas, french fries dan cheese-cinnamon coffee (rekomendasi dari barista yang ternyata emang seenak itu   ). Sempet komplain ke waitress karna ada orderan yang kurang sesuai, ternyata mereka welcome banget sama kritik dari konsumen, no baper and no drama! Gak expect ternyata langsung dikasih kompensasi for free, what a great service!! Love sekali
review_translated_text: I came here on April 27 2024 at around 10 am because I happened to be on holiday in Serang plus this cafe is the closest to the hotel. The place is cozy, lots of instagrammable spots, and really spacious. The menu is quite varied and the prices are also affordable. I ordered quesadilas, french fries and cheese-cinnamon coffee (recommendation from the barista which turned out to be really that delicious   ). Even though I complained to the waitress because my order wasnt quite right, it turns out they really welcome criticism from consumers, no excitement and no drama! I didnt expect that I was immediately given compensation for free, what a great service!! Love it so much

review_text: Stopped by this cafe because I was staying at the Lynn Hotel Atmosphere and service are okay, food is standard

Bagaimana bisa cafe sebesar dan senyaman ini tidak ada wifi yg tersedia untuk umum? Dan ketika disajikan kentang sosis disertai salad tidak langsung disajikan sendok/garpu? Bagaimana saya makannya jika hanya disediakan tusuk gigi? Agak sulit juga untuk panggil pegawai jika ada keperluan tambahan krn tempatnya luas namun sepertinya pelayannya terbatas. Mungkin harus lebih dipikirkan lagi kebutuhan costumernya. Kopinya oke. Tempatnya nyaman. Harga affordable. Namun agak sulit untuk saya yg datang sendiri untuk WFC jika ingin menambah pesanan, karena harus datang ke kasir. Mungkin pesan mandiri via barcode/aplikasi bisa jadi solusi? Semoga bisa jadi masukan
review_translated_text: How can a cafe this big and comfortable not have wifi available to the public? And when you are served sausage potatoes accompanied by salad, are you not immediately served with a spoon/fork? How can I eat it if only toothpicks are provided? Its also a bit difficult to call staff if there are additional needs because the place is large but it seems like there are limited staff. Maybe you should think more about customer needs. The coffee is okay. The place is comfortable. Affordable price. However, its a bit difficult for me to come alone to WFC if I want to add to my order, because I have to go to the cashier. Maybe self-ordering via barcode/app could be a solution? Hopefully this can be input

review_text: kalau ke pasar lama pasti lewatin tempat ini tapi belum pernah cobain karena tujuannya makan bakso. kali ini ke pasar lama cobain juga. pesanan kami 1. Mie aceh tumis --> ini enak mienya rasa karinya medok banget mie nya juga dimasak pas gak kelembekan. bisa pilih level pedes juga dan ada acar bawangnya juga 2. nasi goreng --> pesen yg daging sapi rasanya biasa aja sih bumbu kurang medok kurang rasa 3. martabak aceh yg biasa --> ini kayak martabak telor telor tapi gak kayak yg martabak biasa pake kulit ya ini lebih berasa telornya ada cocolan kari 4. roti cane kuah kari --> rotinya gurih lembut bisa pilih yang manis juga pake susu atau coklat. ini kami pilih yg pake kari. kuah karinya rasanya agak asem ini gak tau ya apa rasanya emang gitu atau ... tempatnya open space gitu cuaca panas banget jadi gak nyaman meja berdebu dan ada asbak rokok di tiap mejanya gak nyaman jadinya pengen cepet2 kelar makan
review_translated_text: If you go to the old market you will definitely pass this place but have never tried it because the goal is to eat meatballs. This time, go to the old market and try it too. our order 1. Stir-fried Acehnese noodles --> these noodles are delicious, the curry flavor is really medok, the noodles are also cooked just right, theyre not soft. You can choose the spicy level too and there are pickled onions too 2. Fried rice --> ordered the beef, it just tasted normal but the spices werent medok and lacked flavor 3. Regular Aceh martabak --> this is like egg martabak but not like the regular martabak with skin, it tastes more like egg with curry sauce 4. Roti cane with curry sauce --> the bread is soft and tasty, you can choose sweet and also use milk or chocolate. We chose the one with curry. The curry sauce tastes a bit sour, I dont know whether it tastes like that or... the place is open space so the weather is really hot so its not comfortable the tables are dusty and there are cigarette ashtrays on each table its not comfortable so I want to finish eating quickly

review_text: Tempat makan yang enak dan nyaman untuk keluarga atau siapapun yang lagi laper. Saya pribadi cuma sempat pesan jus tomat disini yang rasanya seger, hanya saja seharusnya waktu itu saya pesan tanpa memakai gula biar lebih sehat. Sedangkan teman saya pesan nasi goreng aceh dengan telur dadar. Untuk yang kurang tahan makanan pedas, mungkin perlu request agar tidak terlalu pedas, mengingat makanan Aceh atau sekelasnya kebanyakan menggunakan bumbu dan rasa pedasnya yang sawadikap. Pesan di tempat duduk yang nanti akan diberikan list menu oleh pelayan. Sedangkan untuk membayar via kasir yang ada di depan dekat pintu masuk, belakangan setelah selesai makan.
review_translated_text: A delicious and comfortable place to eat for families or anyone who is hungry. Personally, I only ordered tomato juice here which tasted fresh, but I should have ordered it without sugar so it would be healthier. Meanwhile, my friend ordered Acehnese fried rice with omelet. For those who cant stand spicy food, you may need to request that it not be too spicy, considering that Acehnese food or its class mostly uses sawadikap spices and has a spicy taste. Order at your seat and the waiter will give you a menu list. Meanwhile, you can pay via the cashier at the front near the entrance, later after you finish eating.

review_text: Rekomen banget buat kalian yang mau rame-rame makan sama temen sekedar nongki, atau kolega kerja/bisnis, atau mungkin dengan keluarga. Interior yang mewah dan keren, alat makan yang sangat bagus, dan tempat duduk yang nyaman untuk ngobrol2 dalam jangka waktu yang cukup lama. Untuk makanan dan minuman memang menurut saya cukup mahal, seharga resto-resto yang ada di mall gitu, porsinya juga lumayan sedikit. Tapi plating nya cakep banget dan rasa makanan yang enak ga bikin kecewa. Mungkin ada usulan aja untuk minuman sebisa mungkin dibuat penuh sampai atas gelas (es batu diperbanyak atau minumannya diperbanyak), karena waktu teman saya pesan minuman redvelvet, kira-kira hanya terisi 3/4 gelas lebih dikit.
review_translated_text: Highly recommended for those of you who want to eat together with friends just hanging out, or work/business colleagues, or maybe with family. Very spacious parking, and lots of tables and chairs available (indoor and outdoor). A cafe that I think is very, very comfortable. Luxurious and cool interior, very nice cutlery, and comfortable seating for chatting for quite a long time. In my opinion, food and drinks are quite expensive, for the price of restaurants in malls, the portions are also quite small. But the plating is really nice and the delicious taste of the food wont disappoint. Maybe there is a suggestion to make the drink as full as possible to the top of the glass (more ice cubes or more drink), because when my friend ordered a redvelvet drink, it was only about 3/4 of the glass filled.

Well, usually, when I come for the first time, I always try the most special or signature... or sometimes the most common one is a Coffee latte... But when I came here, I tried one of the signatures, hot Bhumi Milk Coffee. Hmmm... This coffee is prepared with selected coffee, milk and its specialty lies in the sugar, yes, the sugar uses palm sugar. Its quite unique, although for my taste buds, the taste of the coffee is less intense and tasteless, lost to the milk and palm sugar taste. Overall, its fine, and worth enjoying. This stall is open until late at night. If it feels too late to go home, calm down, opposite there is a three star hotel, if you cant afford to pay, next to it there is a prayer room belonging to the Korem... Hahahaha... Happy coffee hunting at Kopi Sanger in Serang City, Banten.

review_text: Dateng for the 1st time kesini sabtu jam 11, masih agak sepi. Tempatnya lumayan enak, kalau cerah bisa pilih outdoor ada area sitting bar untuk menyendiri sambil lihat pemandangan toll. Sayang pas hujan tampias, sebaiknya roof ditambahin. Karena kesini sm suami dan anak, pilih area indoor ber-AC yg adem. Pesan Mie karet ori dan pangsit rebus, karena pake ayam kampung   semua enak dan anak yg batuk jadi bs makan sehat & aman. Mienya kenyal dan ndut jd puas + worth the price. Mie dan pangsit rebus : 8,5/10. Hot Lemon Tea: 8/10 PakSu minum Japanese drip filtered coffee beans natural anaerob :8/10 ada asamnya tapi msh ada body. Kalau kesini lagi cocok pas lagi sepi spt ini. Apalagi hujan gerimis.. feels like home. Tapii kalau tempatnya lg rame mungkin cocok untuk eat&go aja. Pelayanan ramah dan baik barista & waiternya. Recommended? Yes. Visit Again? Yes.
review_translated_text: Came here for the 1st time, Saturday at 11, it was still a bit quiet. The place is quite nice, if its sunny you can choose the outdoor sitting bar area to be alone while looking at the view of the toll road. Unfortunately, when it rains, it would be better to add a roof. Because youre here with your husband and children, choose a cool, air-conditioned indoor area. Order original rubber noodles and boiled dumplings, because they use free-range chicken   everything is delicious and children who have coughs can eat healthily & safely. The noodles are chewy and ndut so Im satisfied + worth the price. Boiled noodles and dumplings: 8.5/10. Hot Lemon Tea: 8/10 PakSu drinks Japanese drip filtered coffee beans natural anaerobic : 8/10 there is acid but it still has body. If you come here again, its suitable when its quiet like this. Especially the drizzling rain... feels like home. But if the place is busy, maybe its suitable for eat&go. Friendly and good service from the baristas & waiters. Recommended? Yes. Visit Again? Yes.

Area outdoornya tersedia di lantai 2, pinggiran danau, dan di taman bawah pohon. Konfigurasi bangkunya pun banyak. Di kedai kopi ini saya memesan menu Susu Regal Rider. Rasanya pas, apalagi ketika biskuit regalnya lumer jadi satu dengan kopinya. Rasanya sayang untuk menyeruput es kopi ini dengan cepat.
review_translated_text: Maybe Coffee Rider is just one of many cafes in Serang, but for me this is the best. Having a very spacious indoor (air-conditioned) and outdoor area, Coffee Rider is suitable for those who need a place to work, discuss or just hang out. The outdoor area is available on the 2nd floor, by the lake, and in the garden under the trees. There are many bench configurations. At this coffee shop I ordered the Regal Rider Milk menu. The taste is just right, especially when the regal biscuits melt into one with the coffee. It would be a shame to sip this iced coffee quickly.

review_translated_text: Long queue for orders, slow service. I ordered at 21.09 and the drink arrived first after waiting a long time. The food order didnt arrive until the drinks were finished. I went to the cashier and confirmed he said the food was in process. At 21.50 I went to the cashier and he said the food had already arrived but the remote didnt sound even though it was. What Im wondering is why my food wasnt delivered or looked for by customers or using information speakers at the middle school until the food was really cold even though at that time there werent many people ordering because it was already late at night. I swear Ive given up on going there again. I dont really recommend the cafe... Learn to serve customers better. Ive paid quite a bit for the food, which is of better quality than the snacks from the carts in elementary school.

review_text: This restaurant unfolds like a dream! Imagine a haven of spaciousness, both indoors and out. Lush greenery tickles the breeze, while the vast parking lot ensures your chariot finds its resting place with ease. Whether you seek the vibrant sunset or the calming shade of trees, a perfect spot awaits. Inside, a symphony of tables welcomes you   plenty of space to dine, mingle, or even orchestrate a power lunch (just try not to silence your fellow diners with operatic pronouncements!). And fear not, hygiene takes center stage   the toilets are sparkling clean and brand new. Just a whispered prayer that the construction of the praying room finishes soon to complete the harmony. Now, onto the culinary concerto! The coffee croons a pleasant tune, neither a discordant screech nor a bland murmur. But the true stars of the show are the delicious food dishes. Each bite dances on your palate, though a touch of saltiness might have the conductor reaching for the salt shaker (a minor adjustment in the kitchen could elevate the performance to perfection!). And lets not forget the grand finale: the price tag. It sings a sweet melody for your wallet, ensuring you leave humming a happy tune. So, should you join this culinary chorus? Absolutely! The spaciousness, serene atmosphere, and delicious food (with a minor salty note) make it a delightful experience. Just remember, the praying room awaits its final bow, and perhaps request a slightly less salty score from the kitchen maestro. Otherwise, its a restaurant that deserves a standing ovation!

review_text: REVIEW UPDATE TERBARU terakhir kali ke Hiji, dari kasir dan waiters nya kacau bgt. Satu, Awal masuk tempat, masa kasir nya jutek bgt. Gada kalimat sapaan macem pagi,siang,malam, atau upselling yg lain. Ini kasir diem aja deh, smpe saya sendiri yg ngomong mau pesen ini aja deh. Saat itu mikir, oh mungkin kasir nya lagi badmood. Dua, waiters nya aneh banget. Saya komplain chiken skin nya bau, dan ga fresh. Setidaknya ada ucapan maaf kek, atau apadeh yah. Ini saat sy komplain, cuma ambil chiken skin nya doang lgsng balik badan. Wah gila sih, baru kali ini service nya jelek banget. Sayang banget loh, padahal makanan dan kopinya enak. Tp kecewa bgt sama service nya. Selama ini gada tuh di tempat caffe lain yg service nya jelek bgt. Payah nih pdhl sebelumnya saya review ini bagus bgt loh kacau nih Tempatnya enak, luas banget. parkirannya juga luas jadi ga susah buat nyari parkir baik motor dan mobil. untuk minumannya kemanisan sih, dan rasa nya kurang cocok aja di saya. tapi kalo kopi susu nya enak yang tilu. tempatnya emang agak kurang cocok aja buat yang jompo, krn gabisa senderan. tapi untuk design tribunnya lumayan lah.. selebihnya good

review_translated_text: LATEST UPDATE REVIEW Last time I went to Hiji, the cashier and waiters were really chaotic. One, when you first entered the place, the cashier was really rude. There are no greetings such as morning, afternoon, evening, or other upselling. The cashier just kept quiet, until I said I wanted to order this. At that time I thought, oh maybe the cashier is in a bad mood. Two, the waiters are really strange. I complained that the chicken skin smelled and wasnt fresh. At least theres an apology, Grandpa, or whatever. This is when I complained, I just took the chicken skin and immediately went back. Wow, thats crazy, this is the first time the service is really bad. Its a shame, even though the food and coffee are delicious. But really disappointed with the service. So far, there are no other cafes where the service is really bad. Thats bad Even though I previously reviewed this, its really good this is messed up The place is nice, very spacious. The parking lot is also spacious so its not difficult to find parking for both motorbikes and cars. the drink is sweet, and the taste just doesnt suit me. but if the coffee with milk is delicious then its tilu. The place is a bit unsuitable for the elderly, because you cant lean back. but for the design of the stands its not bad... the rest is good

review_text: Malam Minggu & hari Minggu malam sempat mampir ke Warung Kontainer setelah sekian lama pandemi.. untuk macam ragam kedainya ga berubah ya, gaes.. warung kontainer macam2 tempat jualan ada yg jual dimsum, burger, seafood, takoyaki, kontainer yg menjual khusus kopi racikan jg ada, bahkan ada satu warung kontainer yg jg menjual coffee beer.. lengkap deh pokoknya mah dsini.. tapi kali ini aku order Es Jeruk Sonkit, rasanya unik asem manis seger, gaes     seriuuusss.. kudu nyoba ini gaes.. rasanya ga kya es jeruk biasa apalagi es jeruk peras, bedaa.. Oya, buat pecinta rasa asam & suka bgt es jeruk Sonkit yg betulan asem, bisa kok request ke penjualnya klo gulanya sedikit aja atau ga usah pake gula gitu.. Nah, lokasi kedai es jeruk sonkit ini tempatnya bersebrangan sama kedai yg jualan burger ya gaes.. Buat burgernya sorry kelupaan difotoin     haha..   burgernya ramah di kantong bro/sis.. pokoknya siapkan kocek 15rb, di kedai burger ini pun jg jual kebab harganya relatif sama kya harga burgernya.. Untuk kedai Seafood masih sama ya dari segi rasanya tapi masukan saja klo bisa servisnya kya dulu lg, mending seafood buat pembeli yg makan di tempat disajikan ke dalam semacam baskom atau mangkok besar gitu, jadi yg digelar sebagai plastik buat pelindung mejanya itu yg buat bekas kulit2 kerang yg abis dimakan Fyi,  pas malming tetap sama kya dulu sebaiknya jangan datang lebih dari jam 9 mlm yaa.. Pasalnya menu-menu favorit tiap malming udh keburu cepet laris    Sayang bgt, kan udh mo rencana nongki sama kawan2 genknya atau ajakin ayank beb ksana jd krg asik krn kelaparan/kehausan, jangan sampai ya gaes.. Satu lagi, live music nya kereeen, yg jadi penyelenggaranya jg keren betul2 deh pas malam Minggu bs menikmati musik Hits 90s & 2000s.. Thanks Warung Kontainer!!! Dan respect pas live music hari Minggu malamnya pada penontonnya antusias sampe joged2, udah gitu kompak & yg bikin lebih salut joged2 pas bagian musik Ska tapi ga pada cari keributan buat senggol bacok        sehingga penonton cewe pun jadi aman menonton maupun pas mau ikutan jogednya juga..          Saya jadi berasa menonton band pas saat muda dulu (eeeh skrg pun muda jg ding  )
review_translated_text: Sunday evening & Sunday evening I stopped by Warung Kontainer after the pandemic for so long... the variety of shops hasnt changed, guys... container stalls are all kinds of places selling dimsum, burgers, seafood, takoyaki, containers that sell specialty coffee blends Theres also one, theres even a container stall that also sells coffee beer... its basically complete here... but this time I ordered Sonkit Orange Essence, it tastes unique and fresh, sweet and sour, guys     Seriuuusss... I have to try this, guys. . It doesnt taste like regular orange ice, let alone squeezed orange ice, its different... Oh yes, for those who love sour tastes and really like Sonkit orange ice which is really sour, you can ask the seller to use just a little sugar or you dont need to use that kind of sugar... Well, the location of the Sonkit Orange Ice Shop is opposite the shop that sells burgers, guys... For the burgers, sorry I forgot to take a photo     haha...   The burgers are pocket friendly bro/sis... just prepare 15k in your pocket, even at this burger shop Also selling kebabs, the price is relatively the same as the price of a burger... For seafood shops, its still the same in terms of taste, but if you can, the service is like before, its better for customers who eat on the spot to serve seafood in a kind of basin or large bowl, so that what is served as plastic to protect the table is the one that leaves the skin behind. shellfish that have been eaten FYI, during dinner its still the same as before, its best not to come later than 9 pm... Because the favorite menus every evening are selling out fast    Thats a shame, youve already planned to hang out with your friends or take your brother there so its really fun Because youre hungry/thirsty, dont let it happen, guys... One more thing, the live music is cool, the organizers are really cool, on Saturday nights you can enjoy music hits from the 90s & 2000s... Thanks Warung Kontainer!!! And respect for the live music on Sunday nights, the audience is enthusiastic to the point of jogging, its already so unified & what makes it even more respectful is dancing during the Ska music part but not looking for a fuss to bang and bang        so the female audience is safe watching too or when I want to join in the jogging too..          I feel like I watched the band when I was young (eeeh now Im young too ding  )

review_translated_text: One of the Fancy Restaurants in the BSD area. Located on the Nusantara Hall, 2nd floor, ICE BSD Main building. review_text: Biasanya mampir sini setiap ada Big Bad Wolf. Restonya baru buka Maret 2021, tapi sudah melayani catering dari Juni tahun lalu. Kalo suka ikan ada salmon Wellington yang dilumuri spinach cream, trus dibungkus pastry renyah banget. Minta dill saucenya rada hangat biar makin nikmat. Nyobain pizza salame e rucola. Ada nasi pagedangan, nasinya beraroma rempah kayak liwet, lauknya jg banyak, ga abis sendiri jg. Minumnya nyobain exotic blue, tomahawk yg manis, sama pineapple mojito tails yg suegeer bgt. review_translated_text: Usually stop here every time there is a Big Bad Wolf. The restaurant only opened in March 2021, but has been providing catering since June last year. If you like fish, there is salmon Wellington coated in spinach cream, then wrapped in really crunchy pastry. Ask for the dill sauce to be slightly warm so that it is even more delicious. Try the salame e rucola pizza. Typical Italian thin pizza, with lots of salami topping. These two menus can make five of us still full. Cant eat if you havent eaten rice? There is pagedangan rice, the rice smells of spices like liwet, there are lots of side dishes, you cant finish it alone either. Try exotic blue, sweet tomahawk, and pineapple mojito tails which are really suege. Oh, you can park in front of the Nusantara lobby, just tell the security guarding the door. There is also a pool table if you want to hang out after eating with friends. The place is nice, a bit quiet because its not in a mall. But its still busy at night and on weekends.

review_text: Kacau banget terakhir reservasi di sini.  Reservasi ke nomor yg ada di instagram.  Terus dioper ke nomor lain.  Terus responnya ga cerdas dan lugas.  Capek banget konfirmasinya.  Reservasi utk iftar.  Jam 6 lewat sampe udh wkt buka makanan blm ada samaa sekali.  Minum pun ga ada.  Mau batalin puasa pake sanqua gelas.  Makanan baru diserve satu satu jam set 7. Dan minuman dateng baru jam 7. Ada satu pesanan yg dipesan khusus utk vegan,  malah pas diaduk banyak daging cincangnya.  Di situ ada mushroom dan mashroom ga ada.  Bener2 cuma mie tok.  Minta ganti baru.  Ttp ada dagingnya.  Dan sayurannya jg ga ada.  Udh tau buat vegan malah ditawarin diganti bakso sapi.  Wkwk.  Akhirnya minta diganti aja ketiga kali minta ditambah keju aja.  Dicobain malah pahit banget rasanya.  Not recommended sih.  Kapok banget. Padahal harganya ga murah ya.
review_translated_text: The last reservation here was really messy. Make a reservation via the number on Instagram. Continue to pass to another number. Then the response is not intelligent and straightforward. Very tired of confirmation. Reservations for iftar. After 6 oclock until it was time to open, there was no food at all. Theres no drinking either. Want to break the fast using sanqua glass. The food wasnt served until around 7. And the drinks arrived at 7. There was one order specifically for vegans, but when it was stirred, there was a lot of minced meat. There are mushrooms there and there are no mushrooms. Really, its just noodles. Ask for a new replacement. But theres meat. And there are no vegetables either. I already know that for vegans they are even offered to replace it with beef meatballs. Wow. Finally asked for it to be replaced, the third time I asked to just add cheese. When I tried it, it tasted really bitter. Not recommended though. Very tired. Even though the price is not cheap, yes.

review_translated_text: I swear this is the worst iced tea branch Ive ever encountered. 2x ordered less sugar less ice and gave it normal. And the last time I ordered more less sugar, less ice, the receipt was correct, the lady was wearing a hijab, which made it wrong, I heard her say, Well, it should be less sugar, then the cashier, a girl whose eyes were a bit slanted, actually took it to me. When I took it, I said make sure: this is really less sugae and less ice, right? He answered yes, thats right. When I tried it, it was really sweet and there was a lot of ice. It really makes you emotional. Im sorry to buy again here. Hopefully the owner will read this so that the employees can be briefed on what the customer asks for, it must be given as requested, dont just give it in vain. POOK, for other customers, the main thing is that if you buy again at this branch, you have to really look at it before they will complain to the person who made it.

review_text: Kenal Mesona Cincau Hitam ini dari hampers yang diberikan pada saat acara pertemuan keluarga. Karena penasaran, kita rela menjelajah sampai ke Serpong untuk mengetahui restonya. Ya, mereka baru memiliki satu cabang saja. Berikut menu yang kita pesan: 1. Cincau cendol gula aren 2. Kopi cincau 3. Susu aren cincau serut 4. Mini puding 16 pcs Untuk rasa cincaunya enak dengan pertemanan saus manis susunya. Ini cincau hitam ya dan pada saat dikonsumsi ada rasa gerus2 pasir pahit ciri khas cincau hitam yang menambah citra rasa. Untuk kopi cincaunya kami kurang cocok dengan selera, tetapi susu aren cincau serutnya enak banget. Sebaiknya order yang cincau serut ya agar mudah diminum menggunakan sedotan boba. Kita pulang membawa oleh-oleh mini puding yang berisi 16 pcs cincau puding untuk nanti dinikmati di rumah dengan keluarga.
review_translated_text: Get to know Mesona Cincau Hitam from the hampers given at family gatherings. Out of curiosity, we were willing to explore as far as Serpong to find out about the restaurant. Yes, they only have one branch. Heres the menu we ordered: 1. Palm sugar cendol grass jelly 2. Grass jelly coffee 3. Shaved palm grass jelly milk 4. Mini pudding 16 pcs The grass jelly tastes delicious with the sweet milk sauce. This is black grass jelly and when consumed there is a bitter gritty taste characteristic of black grass jelly which adds to the taste. We didnt like the grass jelly coffee, but the shaved grass jelly palm milk was really delicious. Its best to order shaved grass jelly so its easy to drink using a boba straw. We went home with a mini pudding souvenir containing 16 pieces of grass jelly pudding to enjoy at home with the family.

review_text: Wah ini enak dan tidak guilty saat makan. Sudah beberapa kali saya kesini untuk cari dessert yang tidak terlalu manis. Saya suka cincau mesona nya, cendolnya jg enak. Boleh dicoba ya teman2.
review_translated_text: Wow, this is delicious and not guilty when eating. Ive been here several times looking for a dessert that isnt too sweet. I like the mesona grass jelly, the cendol is also delicious. You can try it, friends.

review_text: Hmm pengalaman pertama kurang menyenangkan disini, saya dan 5 teman datang untuk bermain game kartu dan makan minum, lalu didatangi oleh seorang yang nyebut dirinya mamang lalu berkata kalau mau gini gini harus ijin, sama mamang atau sama yang jualan yang mana aneh, karena kami hanya bermain game sambil makan minum, lalu mamang ini bbrp saat kemudian datang untuk mengusir kami dengan menanyakan berapa lama lagi mau disini?, yang mana tidak sopan menurut saya dan teman teman. Okelah jika kami hanya hanya numpang bermain saja, kami disini juga beli makan dan minum seperti pelanggan lain, dan keadaan foodcourt pun masih sepi, sungguh pengalaman yang tidak menyenangkan, karena baru kali ini di foodcourt kami bermain seperti ini, saya saja sampai tidak jadi memesan makanan lagi, padahal posisi lapar lagi, tapi apa boleh buat, sudah diusir ya kami pergi. Jika memang ada aturan yang melarang seperti itu, ya boleh silahkan ditempel dengan pengumuman atau apalah, kami menghormati aturan tersebut, tapi dengan posisi kami tidak mengganggu pelanggan lain dan bertransaksi di food court ini lalu ada orang yang seakan akan sebagai penanggung jawab alias mamang, sebagai pelanggan jujur saja saya dan teman teman tersinggung dan memutuskan untuk tidak kembali kesini lagi.
review_translated_text: Hmm, the first experience was not pleasant here, 5 friends and I came to play card games and eat and drink, then we were approached by someone who called himself mamang and said if you want to do this, you have to get permission from your mom or the one selling it which is strange , because we were just playing games while eating and drinking, then a few moments later this mamang came to throw us out by asking how long do you want to stay here?, which was rude in my opinion and my friends. Its okay if were just playing around, were also here buying food and drinks like other customers, and the food court is still quiet, its really an unpleasant experience, because this is the first time weve played at a food court like this, so I didnt even order. more food, even though I was hungry again, but what could I do, we had been kicked out so we left. If there is a rule that prohibits something like that, yes, please put it up with an announcement or whatever, we respect the rule, but in our position we dont disturb other customers and make transactions at this food court and there are people who seem to be in charge, aka mamang , as customers to be honest, my friends and I were offended and decided not to come back here again.
